# Bill Manager Documentation

This document shows how to run the app and screenshots of each feature.

## Setup

1. Install dependencies for the server and client:
   ```bash
   npm install
   npm install --prefix client
   ```
2. Start the development servers:
   ```bash
   npm run dev
   ```
   This runs the API at `http://localhost:3001` and the React frontend at `http://localhost:5173`.

## Building for production

Run the following commands to create a production build and preview it:
```bash
npm run build --prefix client
npm run preview --prefix client
```
